{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"dc62bffc8b","title":"对《清华大学物理教研组对待教师宁“左”勿右》一文的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"fcd7901479","index":0,"year":1958,"month":12,"day":22,"articleId":"dc62bffc8b"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1958.1-1960）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2f2b4f2da3","type":"paragraph","text":"七律和柳亚子先生","index":0,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b"},{"id":"654a8cd4e2","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年四月二十九日三十一年，（三十一年还旧国，落花时节读华章）一九一九年离开北京，一九四九年还北京。旧国之国：都城。不是Ltoho（国家），也不是Country（首都））","index":1,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b"},{"id":"fa0ed2d1ca","type":"paragraph","text":"浣溪沙和柳亚子先生","index":2,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b"},{"id":"7fa3ff9a39","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五〇年十月乐奏。（万方乐奏有于间）这里课置为“秦乐”，应改。（现版已改正）","index":3,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b"},{"id":"1a9b79d3c5","type":"paragraph","text":"水调歌头游泳","index":4,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b"},{"id":"760b860993","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五六年六月长沙水：（才饮长沙水）","index":5,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b"},{"id":"a5c37ef416","type":"paragraph","text":"“常德山山有德，长沙水水无沙”。所谓长沙水，在常德东，有一个有名的“白","index":6,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b"},{"id":"a7919f7ec2","type":"paragraph","text":"民谣：（才饮长沙水）沙井”。武昌鱼：（又食武昌鱼）","index":7,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b"},{"id":"bfc5d11a49","type":"paragraph","text":"三国孙权一度从京口（江）迁都武昌，官、绅士、地主及富裕阶层不悦，反对迁都，造出口号云。“宁饮扬州（建业）水，不食武属鱼”。那时的扬州人，心情如此，现在改变了。武昌但是顺有味道的。","index":8,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b"},{"id":"d04947d329","type":"paragraph","text":"对《清华大学物理教研粗对待教师","index":9,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b"},{"id":"6dafbb2cfa","type":"paragraph","text":"宁“左”勿右》一文的批示","index":10,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b"},{"id":"3c8ac87b4d","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九五八年十二月二十二日）XXX同志","index":11,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b"},{"id":"8e8df4664e","type":"paragraph","text":"建议将此件印发给全国一切大专学校，科学研究机关的党委、总支、支委阅读，并讨论一次，端正方向，争取一切可能争取的教授、讲师、助教、研究人员，为无产阶级的教育事业和文化科学事业服务，你看如何？文学艺术团体、报社杂志社和出版机关的党委、总变）也应发去，也应讨论一次，定。","index":12,"publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b"}],"page":{"id":"000424f571","publicationId":"b2b674a1-9042-4317-a7b8-de4267668ba5","articleId":"dc62bffc8b","start":194,"end":194}}}},"__N_SSG":true}